OL,8,GIn a morning special presentation for
OL,9,Gour younger attendees (although all
OL,10,Gare welcome), we spend Friday morning
OL,11,Gwith WALL-E, one of Pixar's most-loved
OL,12,Gfeatures. In a future where humans
OL,13,Ghave temporarily abandoned Earth, a
OL,14,Gtrash-compacting robot falls in love
OL,15,Gwith a flying droid and helps her on
OL,16,Gher quest to restore hope to mankind.
OL,17,GCharming animation and solid story.
